From: Chen Ni <nichen@iscas.ac.cn>
Date: Thu, 10 Apr 2025 15:34:56 +0800
Subject: Bluetooth: hci_uart: Remove unnecessary NULL check before
 release_firmware()
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
Git-commit: bd3cb3c5aec80f70762c34fdd3068f07b212108e
References: jsc#PED-14261

release_firmware() checks for NULL pointers internally.
Remove unneeded NULL check for fmw here.

Signed-off-by: Chen Ni <nichen@iscas.ac.cn>
Signed-off-by: Luiz Augusto von Dentz <luiz.von.dentz@intel.com>
Acked-by: Chun-Yi Lee <jlee@suse.com>
---
 drivers/bluetooth/hci_aml.c |    3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/bluetooth/hci_aml.c
+++ b/drivers/bluetooth/hci_aml.c
@@ -313,8 +313,7 @@ static int aml_download_firmware(struct
 		goto exit;
 
 exit:
-	if (firmware)
-		release_firmware(firmware);
+	release_firmware(firmware);
 	return ret;
 }
 
